### Models

**`BootstrapperOptions`** — strongly-typed container for all CLI/config inputs.

```csharp
public class BootstrapperOptions
{
    public string Env { get; set; }
    public string Title { get; set; }
    public string Subject { get; set; }
    public string SchemaFile { get; set; }
    public string RegistryUrl { get; set; }
    public bool UpdateRegistry { get; set; }
    public bool DryRun => !UpdateRegistry;
    public string FullSubject => $"{Subject}_{Env}_{Title}";
}
```

**`AvroField`** — represents a single field in an Avro record schema.

```csharp
public class AvroField
{
    public string Name { get; set; }
    public object Type { get; set; }   // string or object[] for unions
    public object Default { get; set; }
}
```

